abstract_str: washington teen andrew crain , 15 , and his friend isaac __yow__ , 16 , helped save the 22-month-old toddler as their fellow teen ran off with her . crain did n't realize it at the time , but the still unnamed culprit was his classmate in a bizarre disguise . the minor has not been identified but the tiny town of __sprague__ is now breathing a sigh of relief the alleged kidnapper has been arrested . it was revealed thursday that the 15-year-old had previously been investigated a year ago for allegedly trying to lure a minor .
